Author: zuumpro
Title: [ANN] ZUUM is Blockchain enabled for Taxi, Ridehsare: UBER alternative **
Body: ZUUM MVP Launched.  ZUUM is UBER Alternative in Blockchain and DeCentralized Economy.   ZUUM is the world’s first decentralized on-demand services platform that allows consumers and service providers to interact directly without intermediaries and ensures fair price based on a smart contract.  ZUUM is a One-Stop platform a variety of OnDemand Services including: Rideshare, Taxi, Roadside Assistance, Auto Service, Cleaning, Nanny, Beauty, General Contractor, and Medical Services.  * No Transaction Fees   http://www.zuum.co  AIRDROP  Simply Download ZUUM Pro or ZUUM Services App and register at ZUUM wallet to get free ICO coins.  You can also buy ZUUM Coins at pre-sale at discounted price from the ZUUM Services App  Download ZUUM Pro App to get free coins (Service Professionals who want to make money by providing transportation, and other services) Download ZUUM Services App to get free coins (Service Consumers who are looking for transportation, and other services)
